Scripter  is an open source free to use android application 
The main point for this application is to simplify the way users will run scripts in android device 
 
If you have an issue, suggestion or question please use 'Issues' option here in github

For more infomation on the application head over to
http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=714834 - in English
